data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the serene Bloomingdale Ridge community! This immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is nestled on a conservation lot, providing a tranquil and  picturesque setting. Key features of this home include a recently replaced roof in 2021, a brand new gas water heater installed in April 2022, and recently replaced kitchen appliances. The air  conditioning system is equipped with an ultraviolet light, ensuring a fresh and allergen-free environment. Step into the front living area, adorned with newly installed carpet and a fresh coat of  paint, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. Enjoy an abundance of natural light throughout the home, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance.  The family room boasts sliders leading to the expansive 40 ft long covered back patio. This screened-in paradise offers a breathtaking conservation view, ensuring privacy with no rear  neighbors. Imagine unwinding or entertaining guests in this delightful outdoor space.  Inside, discover the thoughtfully designed split-bedroom plan. The two bedrooms share a hall bath, and the hallway features two closets for linen and additional storage. The master bedroom is  a retreat in itself, featuring a spacious walk-in closet and a slider opening to the patio.  Convenience is at its best with an inside laundry area leading seamlessly to the garage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours – schedule a viewing today and experience the  perfect blend of style, functionality, and natural beauty!
